chrs is the csus common human resources system, built in peoplesoft hcm 9.2. this system manages all aspects of an employees records at sjsu including position, job and personal data; temporary academic employment; student employment; benefits; time and absence data; and more. all csu campuses will exist in one database. sjsu is part of the second wave of campuses implementing the new system and will begin the project in june of 2021. the system is set to go live in december of 2022. to learn more, visit thechancellors office chrs website.chrs will be an upgraded version of peoplesoft (hr only) that is shared with all other csu campuses and the chancellors office.to learn more about the anticipated changes, please seechrs changes.university-personnel@sjsu.eduup north:408-924-2450up south:408-924-2250up webmasterup northadministration building 242up southupd building 3rd floor